keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
mapkey ' `
unmap d
unmap u
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
unmap J
unmap K
unmap gT
unmap gt
map <space>h previousTab
map <space>l nextTab
unmap h
unmap l
map zh scrollLeft
map zl scrollRight
unmap T
map <space>sb Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map gt visitPreviousTab
unmap r
map R reload
unmap f
unmap F
map gd LinkHints.activateMode
map gx LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
unmap x
unmap X
map <space>bb removeTab
map <space>br restoreTab
unmap <a-p>
map <space>bp togglePinTab
unmap yt
map <space>by duplicateTab
